title: (Thurs Early Bird) What Lunchbox saw at the Grocery Store That He’s Never Seen Before and it BLEW HIS MIND + Elder Vs. Millennial + Mailbag: Listener Doesn’t Want To Go Clubbing in Her 30’s On Bachelorette Party
itunes:title: (Thurs Early Bird) What Lunchbox saw at the Grocery Store That He’s Never Seen Before and it BLEW HIS MIND + Elder Vs. Millennial + Mailbag: Listener Doesn’t Want To Go Clubbing in Her 30’s On Bachelorette Party
description:
Lunchbox couldn't believe what he saw at the grocery store and he came in blazing to tell us about it. He was also recognized by a listener and brought in audio. Eddie and Morgan face off in Elder versus Millennial with the new twist of stealing questions! A listener in her 30’s needs advice on how to get out of going to the club for a bachelorette party.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
